long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An extension optimized for StackOverflow. It will automatically store your StackOverflow tabs, so you can check them later.

You can organize your links into projects, edit your projects, and reorganize and delete links.
